events.name: Stanford Cardinal at Oregon State Beavers

headlines.description: Keller Chryst threw a 3-yard touchdown pass to JJ Arcega-Whiteside with 20 seconds left and No. 20 Stanford survived Bryce Love's absence for a 15-14 come-from-behind victory over Oregon State on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 20 Stanford comes back for 15-14 win over Oregon State

video.headline: Stanford squeaks by Oregon State with late TD

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Stanford squeaks by Oregon State with late TD) 2017/10/26 ESHEET

events.name: Eastern Michigan Eagles at Northern Illinois Huskies

headlines.description: Marcus Jones had the only touchdown in overtime and Northern Illinois scored on three of its final four drives to rally past Eastern Michigan 30-27 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: NIU rallies from 14-point deficit, tops EMU 30-27 in OT

events.name: Toledo Rockets at Ball State Cardinals

headlines.description: Diontae Johnson made four catches for a career-high 170 yards and two touchdowns, and returned a punt 87 yards for a score to help Toledo cruise past Ball State 58-17 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Johnson's 3 TDs lead Toledo past Ball State 58-17

video.headline: Rockets' Johnson runs 87 yards for TD

events.name: South Alabama Jaguars at Georgia State Panthers

headlines.description: Conner Manning threw for 195 yards and two touchdowns, and Georgia State held off South Alabama 21-13 on Thursday night for its first win at Georgia State Stadium.
headlines.shortLinkText: Manning throws for 2 TDs, Georgia State tops S Alabama 21-13
